eyeglass frames. (Walton, Atlanta-Journal Constitution) Art
includes a 2-column color photo of two models wearing fashionable
lenses.
</P>
<P>
   GIRL ZONE _ A new web site allows girls to shop for the latest
fashions without going to the mall. (Sturrock, Palm Beach Post) Art
includes a 6-pica color photo of the Web site logo.
</P>
<P>
   SUMMER VERSATILITY _ From daytime to night, designers are
thinking versatility for summer fashion. (Hernandez, N.Y. Times
News Service)
</P>
