   WITH: PUBLISHING NOTES -- The sun is shining bright on author
Jane Heller, knows by many as the queen of beach books. (O'Briant,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   WITH: PREVIEW -- A look at new titles coming to bookstores in
coming weeks. (Staff, Cox News Service)
</P>
