   WITH: SKUBE ON BOOKS -- The new book ``From Dawn to Decadence''
chronicles the West as victim of its own success. (Skube, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) Art includes a 6-pica color photo of book
jacket.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: N.Y. TIMES BEST SELLERS LIST
</P>
<P>
   SKUBE-ON-BOOKS _ Michael Skube on Howard Bahr's novel of the
Civil War, ``The Year of Jubilo.'' (Skube, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 32.
</P>
<P>
   EDs: Embargoed until 0611.
</P>
