(StMurray, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 19.
</P>
<P>
   EDs: Embargoed until 0611.
</P>
<P>
   POTTER-BOOK _ It's exactly a month until the newest Harry Potter
book comes out, and waiting lists are already filling up. We check
with local booksellers to find out how big the frenzy is so far.
(Barchas, Austin American-Statesman). MOVED.
</P>
