car and hotel reservations.
</P>
<P>
   Ease of use: Some slowness, but storefront is inviting and easy
to peruse.
</P>
<P>
   Telephone response: ``Kim'' picked up right away, but she wasn't
happy about it. ``I'll have to look,'' she grumped.
</P>
<P>
