</P>
<P>
   Telephone response: Picked up in 30 seconds. Response to a
question was ``I don't know.''
</P>
<P>
   E-mail response: Sent a preformulated response that had nothing
to do with our question.
</P>
<P>
   Features: Loads of cruise specials. Promises e-mailed promotions
that are so ``hot and time sensitive'' that they can't appear on
