   &UR; AUTOMOTIVE (l, f) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   AUTOS-COLUMN (Undated) _ Readers write, suspicious about
nefarious uses of Night Vision, angry that I even review SUVs and
pickup trucks, wondering why their tires are lasting so long. By
Royal Ford.
