<TEXT>
<P>
   BC-NJ-ROUKEMA-NYT (moved on Monday, May 22)
</P>
<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Monday, May 22,
about the Republican primary in New Jersey for the seat held by
Representative Marge S. Roukema misstated the criticism leveled at
her by the Club for Growth, a conservative group based in
Washington. (The error was repeated in an article in some copies on
Wednesday.) While the organization has objected to Roukema's
moderate stands on welfare reform and tax issues, it has not
criticized her for supporting abortion rights; it takes no position
on social issues.  &QL;
</P>
