</P>
<P>
   MARCHFIRST-AD-COLUMN (New York) _ MarchFirst, a recently formed
company offering a wide variety of Internet professional services,
seeks to stand out amid competitors ranging from management
consultants to advertising agencies to Web site builders. By Stuart
Elliott.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET.)
</P>
<P>
   BIZGLANCE (Undated) _ Digest of the day's financial stories.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET.)
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times is using wires stories on the stock and bond
markets.
</P>
